reviewText: Very overpriced for what you get
The quality of this tape is disappointing; it is not very clear (fuzzy) and must have been one of her first tapes by the way it was recorded.

This is one of Joanie's unscary workouts. It's perfect for the beginner to intermediate exerciser. It's very fun to do and not to daunting to keep up with. The upper body portion of the workout helped to reduce the pain I suffer in my left shoulder. This is a workout you can stick with for awhile.
